{"tid":314118,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工人涉跟蹤非禮女生","createTime":"2017-07-09T01:58:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-09T04:57:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"459c5a9f3729d4ff2e8184ab19799a42bf66d690","tid":314118,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T01:58:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20083796&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170709\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20083796%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170709&d=9K4m331hoOOF5Vr9VFkABaMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=3f58106b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20083796%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170709&h=3f03758e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20083796&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170709</a><br />\n<br />\n工人涉跟蹤非禮女生<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n九龍城法院<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】六旬地盤工人在兩個月內，涉兩度跟蹤住同一大廈的18歲女學生回家，並趁對方打開大門一刻從後撲出，捉着對方肩膀說「見到你，我好開心」，又問「夠唔夠錢使」，其間涉摸她的胸。案件昨在九龍城法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n問「夠唔夠錢使」<br />\n<br />\n64歲被告吳智慧被控兩項非禮罪，他暫毋須答辯。控罪指他在今年5月20日及本月4日，在華荔邨一個單位內非禮女事主X。控方表示需時調查，包括取得閉路電視片段及做認人手續。裁判官拒被告擔保申請，案件8月4日在西九龍法院再提訊，其間被告還柙。<br />\n據了解，5月20日首次案發時，被告疑跟蹤X入升降機，尾隨對方，待X開門入屋時突然走入單位，說「見到你，我好開心」，又問「夠唔夠錢使」，X反抗，其間感到胸部被摸。第二次案發當日，被告涉重拖故技，並成功進入X家。警方後來根據閉路電視紀錄拘捕被告。<br />\n案件編號：KCCC2060/17<br />\n■記者歐陽聯發"},{"pid":"ad66a22c68aefd4413425face4f9058c7d5f4df3","tid":314118,"uid":102056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T01:59:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"01f391bbb992dd3f35319da234f5af15f1f8f75f","tid":314118,"uid":77259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:02:07.000Z","msg":"吳智慧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87007d1d91ca0f4c4096b0103805306cbedb3350","tid":314118,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:39:03.000Z","msg":"等睇人話勞資糾紛"},{"pid":"318067318451d6aab3531db877de1f67a33ca9aa","tid":314118,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:50:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吳智慧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解一般市民就開全名<br />\n達官貴人就唔開全名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0415643bf31ce59abeb72943ee4d2f11b918d08a","tid":314118,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:51:13.000Z","msg":"無智慧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b04ed6e32fa6f9255b6fc29494b0b881eef9c8","tid":314118,"uid":15370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:54:22.000Z","msg":"廢老"},{"pid":"02f0d89adf07b8f8bf76a99d39eb83a7d5d86a21","tid":314118,"uid":20256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:57:55.000Z","msg":"吳智慧<br />\n好名黎<br />\n佢真係冇腦"}]}